propter

secundum

Secundum is the regular translation of κατά, and as such acquires new meanings. It regularly means according to. In 1 ε 20 De Gen. ad lit. secundum=sub. In 2 :8 notes secundum is the equivalent of ad, near to. Cf. Loc. 1: 5: Plantavit Deus paradisum secundum orientem quod latini habent ad orientem.
